.Sh CAVEATS
On headless iMacs with the LCD panel disconnected, the SMC may enter a
thermal panic mode due to missing temperature sensors
.Pq e.g.\& TL0P, TL1P ,
asserting PROCHOT and throttling the CPU to its minimum frequency.
The
.Va thermal_status
sysctl can be used to diagnose this condition.
Fan manual mode overrides can be used to manage fan speeds in this
scenario.
